1. /etc/dnsmasq.conf:

	no-resolv

	interface=wlan0
	dhcp-range=192.168.15.3,192.168.15.30

2. Networkmanager settings
	Connection Name: <Your Choice>
	Wi-Fi Tab
		Mode: Shared AP
		SSID: <Your SSID>
	Wi-Fi-Security Tab
		Security: WPA & WPA2 Personal
		Password: <your password> / select 'Store the password for all users'
	IPv4 Settings Tab
		Method: Manual
		Address: 192.168.15.1 Mask: 255.255.255.0
	IPv4 Settings Tab
		Method: Ignore

3. Connect to Hidden Wi-Fi Network -> select name enetered above
